Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:40.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:51.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:57.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:04.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:07.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.51,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Responding to an emergency signal, Luffy and the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,others were heading to the other side of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Nami and the others were held captive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in a mysterious facility on Punk Hazard Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to this island to rescue my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind cutting thousands if they get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--There! --Shoot! Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that'll be far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save the Children! The Straw Hats Start to Fight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:32.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,THE ICE LANDS - A MYSTERIOUS FACILITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:38.11,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,BISCUIT ROOM SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the island's day-care or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so big but are they Giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we come to an island of Giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are not-so-big ones too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a multi-racial nursery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be the ones who got frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--Frozen? --What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystery of the island deepens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...A robot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--I love robots! --They're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The best?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot! Robot! Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot! Robot! Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids. So you really love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...my armored self?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me about "the ones who got frozen."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's a stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stuffed raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Help me! --I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky is so popular among boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiral eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're right! --So weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A stag-beetle robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change my hairstyle as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is another hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With this I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...pick my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, somebody, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a child named Momonosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The severed-head talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kids, tell me about this facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get any information out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scaring them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The door to the Biscuit Room is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming! Let's run to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be those pirates! Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of facility is this? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a boy named Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got hit by a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dishonor to a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I should commit ritual suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead! Just stop whining! You male chauvinist pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Those damn escapees! --You can't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy! We're not allowed to use guns and explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Use as few gas canisters as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hit a child, the Master will be furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.43,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Do you really wanna cross this lake, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:55.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,THE BURNING LANDS LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we cross it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some parts are burning but there are ice flows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature could be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all sweaty so let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin and I can't swim so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying I should carry you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop looking at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Zoro wouldn't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already stretching for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that, if we don't cross it, we have to go all the way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice. All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure-Kill Green Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fan Grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boaty Banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a boat! That's awesome, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can use this Fan Grass as an oar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have many kinds of seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a whole bunch of weird plants on the Bowin Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The deeper I went into the dangerous areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the more handy plants I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I survived on that islands for two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no difficulty that I can't overcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get on board already, Usopp! --Or we'll leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm the one who supplied the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To the land of snowcones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you rowing, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so windy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's a headwind! --No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a big difference in temperature on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes for strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is boiling around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were swimming, it would've been horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's so slow! --Why don't you row then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away! Wait, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That centaur again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you change your mind and decide to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you recruiting again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop asking strange creatures to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy on the Snail said "Boss," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The intruders are going that way! Please finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something appeared on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the emergency signal was meant for that Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he shouldn't mean us any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a man with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that the samurai who cut our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now kids, move out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stay out of the way. --It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Robot-san! Did you come from outside the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course! But I'm a cyborg, little guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, our ship - the Sunny is the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is not a day-care?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not sick anymore! We are all fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick? What kind of sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all scary people! You need to stay away from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? They didn't seem like bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They fooled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the stag-beetle robot is a villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--Same for Raccoon Dog-chan? --Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man with the spiral eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so let us protect you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We will protect you sick kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will put them to sleep with our cloud guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, please! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, kids, you need to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I have to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's take them with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy! We don't even know how to save ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can take that many kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is this?! I have a feeling - something tragic is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,come back later and help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew! Even if I've never been out of this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing on this island, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no city! There is no one else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why nobody comes to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see my father and my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to help us later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's help these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure they need saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They said those kids are sick so this could be a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We just met them and we don't know what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not our job to help every single person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you're saying but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can't turn your back on a child crying for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,--They'll get away if nothing is done! --Those brats are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares! Shoot the brats too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--But the Master will... --Better than letting them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiral Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Diable Jambe: Collier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kung Fu Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon Dog-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...stopped running!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind to kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's only kind to kids but I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm falling for her even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper, you go ahead with Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the beautiful lady and the Kung Fu Raccoon Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight our pursuers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing this to answer Nami-san's beautiful wish to help you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't like you all precisely because Nami-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,cares about you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiral Bro, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, brat! Just run already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! They're taking the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting down Armored Franky fans is not an option for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.92,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Snow! Snow! I love playing with snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:17.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,IN FRONT OF THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY BROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.97,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,It's a great way to kill time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-san told me to wait here but what's taking them so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! Snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rearrange its eyes and nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who is it? Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,J...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami and Chopper frantically push through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the mysterious facility to save the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,While Sanji and Franky fight for their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook is at the mercy of the powerful torso samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,until finally, the two begin their duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. the Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
